OL,3,CCharing Cross Met Police sacked
OL,4,Cfollowing "floridly racist" comments
OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police officer who
OL,7,Fworked at Charing Cross police station
OL,8,Fhas been sacked after he was secretly
OL,9,Ffilmed making "floridly racist"
OL,10,Fcomments and "glorifying the use of
OL,11,Finappropriate force".
OL,13,FThe footage, gathered undercover for a
OL,14,FBBC Panorama documentary, appears to
OL,15,Fshow Pc Philip Neilson refer to an
OL,16,Fimmigrant who had overstayed his visa
OL,17,Fwhile off-duty, saying "either put a
OL,18,Fbullet through his head or deport
OL,19,Fhim", the hearing in south London was
OL,20,Ftold on Thursday.
