OL,3,CCharing Cross Met Police sacked
OL,4,Cfollowing "floridly racist" comments
OL,6,FPc Neilson breached the standards of
OL,7,Fprofessional behaviour in respect of
OL,8,Fauthority, respect and courtesy;
OL,9,Fdiscreditable conduct; and equality
OL,10,Fand diversity, the hearing was told.
OL,12,FChairman of the hearing, Commander
OL,13,FJason Prins, said he was satisfied the
OL,14,Fbreaches of conduct amounted to gross
OL,15,Fmisconduct and Pc Neilson was
OL,16,Fdismissed without notice.
OL,18,FPc Neilson is one of ten Charing Cross
OL,19,Fpolice station officers answering
OL,20,Fallegations that surfaced from a BBC
OL,21,FPanorama investigation.
